Did you know that the data expense that ads waste can be up to quadruple?
AdBlock X Protector saves the data expense that ads waste up to 4 times through blocking ads, and makes web surfing up to 3 times faster. Also lighter web surfing increases your battery life up to 21%.

Blocks ads
• Saves up to 50% of your data plan
• Browse up to 2.6x FASTER
• Increase battery life up to 13%

Types of ads block
• Blocks annoying pre-roll video ads
• Blocks ads that hide and then appear
• Blocks ads that suddenly appear
• Blocks ads that waste data
• Blocks sexual ads
• Blocks tracking
• Blocks pop-up ads
• Blocks forced redirects ads
